{
  "id": "adv_event_2210_01_05_02",
  "title": "星の海の記憶",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、ありがとうございます\nお姉ちゃん、きっと喜んでます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ thank you.\nMy sister must be happy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.0666666667,
      "endTime": 7.907325676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "どうかしら？　あの子なら、私の方がうまく歌えた！\n私に歌わせろって、言ったでしょうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? If it were your sister‚ she'd say‚\nI can sing better!‚ I want to sing!' I think she said like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "endTime": 16.666666666599998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "くすっ、考えることはみんな同じですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ we all think the same.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "endTime": 20.9890250365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "なんのこと？\n……ねえ、琴乃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about?\n… You know‚ Kotono",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "endTime": 25.317014143599998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "私、歌ってる時、一言だけだけど\n麻奈と話せた気がするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was singing‚ I felt like I was able to talk to Mana‚\neven if it was just one word.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5333333333,
      "endTime": 32.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "何を話したんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did you talk about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "endTime": 34.803083840999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "貴方の妹は、貴方に負けないくらい\n生意気ねって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your younger sister is\nas cocky as you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0333333333,
      "endTime": 39.607390617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "あはは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "endTime": 41.166666666599994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "――やるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will do",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5333333333,
      "endTime": 43.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "はい？　何をですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes? What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8,
      "endTime": 46.470317459099995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "アルバムの件。長瀬麻奈の曲を、カバーする件\nやるって言ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the album‚ I said I would do\na cover of Mana Nagase's song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7,
      "endTime": 52.390704075100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "え……え？\n……あ、ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… Eh?\n… Thank‚ Thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8333333333,
      "endTime": 56.9581656064,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11500.000000000007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "中途半端なものを出すつもりはないから\n覚悟しておいて。それじゃ、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no intention of putting out something half-baked‚\nso be prepared. Well then‚ good job",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "endTime": 63.5455834602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい、お疲れ様でした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes! Thank you for your effort!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "endTime": 69.6999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2210_01_05-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃん、そして莉央さん\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… Sister‚ and Rio-san‚\nthank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5,
      "endTime": 76.9229713694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666666667,
      "endTime": 79.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
